#: ../../source/getting_started.md:1
msgid "QTEASY 快速上手指南"
msgstr "QTEASY Quick Start Guide"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:3
msgid "安装与导入"
msgstr "Install and import"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:5
msgid "使用 `pip` 安装（要求 `Python >= 3.9, <3.13`）：部分功能（如全部内置策略、数据库存储等）需要可选依赖，详见 [FAQ](https://qteasy.readthedocs.io/zh-cn/latest/faq.html) 与安装说明。"
msgstr ""
"Install with `pip` (requires `Python >= 3.9, <3.13`): some features (such as all built-in strategies, database storage, etc.) require optional dependencies. See the [FAQ](https://qteasy.readthedocs.io/zh-cn/latest/faq.html) and the installation instructions "
"for details."

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:10
msgid "启动后即可导入 `qteasy` 并查看版本号："
msgstr "After startup, you can import `qteasy` and check the version number:"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:17 ../../source/getting_started.md:42 ../../source/getting_started.md:77 ../../source/getting_started.md:143 ../../source/getting_started.md:225
msgid "输出如下："
msgstr "The output is as follows:"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:24
msgid "一分钟跑通"
msgstr "Get it running in one minute"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:26
msgid "本节将带您完成：配置 `tushare Token` → 下载沪深 300 十年指数数据 → 查看数据与 K 线 → 使用内置 DMA 策略对 000300.SH 做择时回测，并得到一份可用的回测结果。"
msgstr "In this section, you will complete: configure the `tushare Token` → download ten years of CSI 300 index data → view the data and candlestick chart → run a timing backtest on 000300.SH using the built-in DMA strategy, and obtain a usable backtest result."

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:28
msgid "1. 配置 tushare Token"
msgstr "1. Configure the tushare token"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:30
msgid "`qteasy` 默认使用 `Tushare` 下载金融数据。若要下载数据，需要先在系统的启动配置文件中配置 `tushare` 的 API Token（请先在 [`tushare` 官网](https://tushare.pro)注册并获取 Token）。"
msgstr ""
"By default, `qteasy` uses `Tushare` to download financial data. To download data, you must first configure Tushare’s API Token in the system startup configuration file (please register on the [`tushare` official website](https://tushare.pro) first to obtain a "
"Token)."

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:32
msgid "有两种方式修改启动配置文件："
msgstr "There are two ways to modify the startup configuration file:"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:34
msgid "**方式一：在代码中设置启动配置**   在首次下载数据前执行`update_start_up_setting()`修改启动配置并自动将其保存到启动配置文件中："
msgstr "**Method 1: Set the startup configuration in code**   Before downloading data for the first time, run `update_start_up_setting()` to modify the startup configuration and automatically save it to the startup configuration file:"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:51
msgid "**方式二：直接修改启动配置文件**   启动配置文件 `qteasy.cfg` 保存在 qteasy 根目录下（可通过 `qt.QT_ROOT_PATH` 查看配置文件路径），使用任意文本编辑器打开该文件并在其中增加一行："
msgstr ""
"**Method 2: Modify the startup configuration file directly**   The startup configuration file `qteasy.cfg` is saved in the qteasy root directory (you can view the config file path via `qt.QT_ROOT_PATH`). Open this file with any text editor and add a line to "
"it:"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:58
msgid "2. 下载 000300.SH 十年指数数据"
msgstr "2. Download 10 years of index data for 000300.SH"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:60
msgid "配置好 `tushare` Token 后，下载沪深 300 指数（000300.SH）的日线数据。建议先下载交易日历与指数基础信息，再下载指数日线（约十年）："
msgstr "After configuring the `tushare` Token, download the daily data of the CSI 300 Index (000300.SH). It is recommended to download the trading calendar and the index basic information first, and then download the index daily data (about ten years):"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:62
msgid "使用`qteasy.refill_data_source()`函数，`qteasy`会自动从配置好的数据下载渠道下载数据，当数据量太大时，会自动分块下载数据、完成数据检查和清洗并存储到数据库中。"
msgstr ""
"Using the `qteasy.refill_data_source()` function, `qteasy` will automatically download data from the configured data source. When the data volume is too large, it will automatically download in chunks, perform data checks and cleaning, and store it in the "
"database."

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:93
msgid "3. 查看数据与 K 线图"
msgstr "3. View the data and candlestick chart"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:95
msgid "数据落地后，可用 `get_history_data` 取数、用 `HistoryPanel.plot` 和 `qt.candle` 画 K 线，确认数据与行情是否正常："
msgstr "After the data has been stored locally, you can fetch it with `get_history_data`, plot candlesticks with `HistoryPanel.plot` and `qt.candle`, and verify whether the data and quotes are normal:"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:112
msgid "3.1 交互式图表（Plotly）与依赖"
msgstr "3.1 Interactive charts (Plotly) and dependencies"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:114
msgid "如果你希望在 Notebook 里缩放、平移并查看每根 K 线/指标对应的具体数值，可以使用交互式绘图："
msgstr "If you want to zoom, pan, and view the specific values corresponding to each candlestick/indicator in a Notebook, you can use interactive plotting:"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:120
msgid "交互式图表依赖 Plotly。建议按你的使用环境选择安装："
msgstr "Interactive charts rely on Plotly. It is recommended to choose the installation based on your usage environment:"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:122
msgid "**基础交互（Plotly Figure）**："
msgstr "**Basic interaction (Plotly Figure)**:"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:128
msgid "**Notebook 更完整交互（FigureWidget + 回调）**："
msgstr "**More complete interaction in Notebook (FigureWidget + callbacks)**:"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:134
msgid "在 Notebook 中，qteasy 会优先尝试提供更完整的 FigureWidget 体验；如果当前内核/依赖不满足，则会回退到 HTML 方式展示。若未安装 Plotly，`interactive=True` 会直接抛出英文错误提示（通常包含 “requires plotly”）。"
msgstr ""
"In a Notebook, qteasy will first try to provide a more complete FigureWidget experience; if the current kernel/dependencies do not meet the requirements, it will fall back to HTML display. If Plotly is not installed, `interactive=True` will directly raise an "
"English error message (usually containing “requires plotly”)."

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:136
msgid "3.2 最常用的交互参数"
msgstr "3.2 Most commonly used interactive parameters"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:138
msgid "`plotly_backend_app='auto'|'FigureWidget'|'html'`：在 Notebook 中选择输出方式（默认 `'auto'`）。"
msgstr "`plotly_backend_app='auto'|'FigureWidget'|'html'`: Select the output mode in a Notebook (default is `'auto'`)."

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:139
msgid "`layout='auto'|'overlay'|'stack'`：多标的布局。`'overlay'` 仅对 **两标的**叠加对比最常用；`'auto'` 会在“两标的 → overlay，其余 → stack”间自动选择。"
msgstr "`layout='auto'|'overlay'|'stack'`: multi-asset layout. `'overlay'` is most commonly used for overlay comparisons of **two assets only**; `'auto'` will automatically choose between “two assets → overlay, otherwise → stack”."

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:140
msgid "`highlight='max'|'min'`：高亮最大/最小值点（静态与交互均可用）。"
msgstr "`highlight='max'|'min'`: Highlight the maximum/minimum value point (available for both static and interactive plots)."

