#: ../../source/getting_started.md:162
msgid "3.5 操作历史数据（HistoryPanel）"
msgstr "3.5 Working with historical data (HistoryPanel)"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:164
msgid "在实际研究中，很多时候我们不仅需要“看 K 线”，还需要**在代码里对历史数据做统计、生成因子**。   `get_history_data()` 除了可以返回 `DataFrame` 外，还可以直接返回一个三维的 `HistoryPanel`，便于对多标的、多指标做统一计算："
msgstr ""
"In practical research, many times we not only need to “look at candlestick charts,” but also need to **compute statistics on historical data and generate factors in code**. In addition to returning a `DataFrame`, `get_history_data()` can also directly return "
"a 3D `HistoryPanel`, making it easy to perform unified calculations across multiple instruments and multiple indicators:"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:200
msgid "上面的例子演示了从 `get_history_data(..., as_data_frame=False)` 得到 `HistoryPanel` 之后，如何在一两行代码内完成**收益率、波动率、技术指标与形态信号**的计算，并随时切回熟悉的 `DataFrame` 做进一步分析。"
msgstr ""
"The example above demonstrates how, after obtaining a `HistoryPanel` from `get_history_data(..., as_data_frame=False)`, you can compute **returns, volatility, technical indicators, and pattern signals** in just one or two lines of code, and switch back at any "
"time to the familiar `DataFrame` for further analysis."

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:202
msgid "更系统的 HistoryPanel 用法可以参考「使用教程」中“历史数据的操作和分析”一章，以及 [HistoryPanel API 参考](api/HistoryPanel.rst)。"
msgstr "For a more systematic guide to using HistoryPanel, see the “Operations and Analysis of Historical Data” chapter in the “User Guide”, as well as the [HistoryPanel API Reference](api/HistoryPanel.rst)."

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:204
msgid "4. 使用 DMA 策略做择时回测"
msgstr "4. Timing backtests using the DMA strategy"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:206
msgid "使用内置 **DMA** 均线择时策略，以 000300.SH 为交易标的，在已下载的十年数据上做回测。下面使用一组常用且表现较稳的参数（短均线 20、长均线 60、DMA 周期 10），直接得到回测结果与图表："
msgstr ""
"Use the built-in **DMA** moving-average timing strategy, with 000300.SH as the trading instrument, and run a backtest on the downloaded 10 years of data. Below, we use a set of commonly used and relatively stable parameters (short MA 20, long MA 60, DMA "
"period 10) to directly obtain the backtest results and charts:"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:269
msgid "![png](img/output_14_1.png)"
msgstr "![png](img/output_14_1.png)"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:271
msgid "运行后将得到收益曲线、最大回撤、夏普比等评价指标及可视化图表。若要尝试其他参数或优化区间，可参考下一节「`qteasy` 能做什么」中的参数优化与 [回测文档](references/3-back-test-strategy.md)。"
msgstr ""
"After running, you will get evaluation metrics such as the equity curve, maximum drawdown, and Sharpe ratio, along with visualized charts. To try other parameters or optimize ranges, refer to the next section “What can `qteasy` do” for parameter optimization "
"and the [backtesting documentation](references/3-back-test-strategy.md)."

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:275
msgid "`qteasy` 能做什么"
msgstr "What can `qteasy` do?"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:277
msgid "**获取并管理金融历史数据**:"
msgstr "**Fetch and manage historical financial data**:"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:279
msgid "方便地从多渠道获取大量金融历史数据，进行数据清洗后以统一格式进行本地存储"
msgstr "Conveniently obtain large amounts of historical financial data from multiple sources, clean the data, and store it locally in a unified format"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:280
msgid "通过`DataType`对象结构化管理金融数据中的可用信息，即便是复权价格、指数成份等复杂信息，也只需要一行代码即可获取"
msgstr "Use the `DataType` object to manage available information in financial data in a structured way. Even for complex information such as adjusted prices and index constituents, you can retrieve it with just one line of code."

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:281
msgid "基于`DataType`对象的金融数据可视化、统计分析以及分析结果可视化"
msgstr "Financial data visualization, statistical analysis, and visualization of analysis results based on `DataType` objects"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:282
msgid "数据本地存储、按需取用，为回测与实盘提供一致的数据基础，便于复现"
msgstr "Store data locally and retrieve it on demand, providing a consistent data foundation for backtesting and live trading, making results easier to reproduce"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:286
msgid "**以简单、安全的方式创建交易策略**"
msgstr "**Create trading strategies in a simple and safe way**"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:288
msgid "通过`BaseStrategy`类，交易策略定义方法直观、逻辑清晰"
msgstr "With the `BaseStrategy` class, the method for defining trading strategies is intuitive and the logic is clear."

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:289
msgid "内置超过70种策略开箱即用，独特的策略混合和组机制，复杂策略可以通过简单策略拼装而来，过程如同搭积木"
msgstr "Over 70 built-in strategies out of the box, plus a unique strategy mixing and grouping mechanism—complex strategies can be assembled from simple ones, like building with blocks."

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:290
msgid "交易策略的数据输入和使用方法完全封装且安全，完全避免无意中导致未来函数、数据泄露等问题，保证策略运行结果的真实性和可靠性"
msgstr "The data inputs and usage methods of trading strategies are fully encapsulated and secure, completely avoiding issues such as inadvertently introducing future functions and data leakage, ensuring the authenticity and reliability of strategy results."

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:291
msgid "同一套策略逻辑既用于回测也用于实盘，减少「回测漂亮、实盘走样」的落差"
msgstr "The same strategy logic is used for both backtesting and live trading, reducing the gap between “great backtest results” and “underwhelming live performance.”"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:293
msgid "![png](img/output_14_3.png)"
msgstr "![png](img/output_14_3.png)"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:295
msgid "**交易策略的回测评价、优化和模拟自动化交易**"
msgstr "**Backtest evaluation, optimization, and simulated automated trading for trading strategies**"

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:297
msgid "通过`Operator`交易员类管理策略运行，按照真实市场交易节奏回测策略，对交易结果进行多维度全方位评价，生成交易报告和结果图表"
msgstr "Manage strategy execution through the `Operator` trader class, backtest strategies according to the real market trading rhythm, evaluate trading results comprehensively across multiple dimensions, and generate trading reports and result charts."

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:298
msgid "提供多种优化算法，包括模拟退火、遗传算法、贝叶斯优化等在大参数空间中优化策略性能"
msgstr "Provides multiple optimization algorithms, including simulated annealing, genetic algorithms, Bayesian optimization, etc., to optimize strategy performance in large parameter spaces."

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:299
msgid "获取实时市场数据，运行策略模拟自动化交易，跟踪记录交易日志、股票持仓、账户资金变化等信息"
msgstr "Fetch real-time market data, run strategy simulations for automated trading, and track and record information such as trading logs, stock positions, and account balance changes."

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:300
msgid "回测、优化与实盘使用同一套运行机制，写一次策略即可全模式运行，配置清晰，便于复现与排查"
msgstr "Backtesting, optimization, and live trading use the same execution mechanism: write a strategy once and run it in all modes, with clear configuration for easy reproduction and troubleshooting."

#: ../../source/getting_started.md:301
msgid "未来将通过QMT接口接入券商提供的实盘交易接口，实现自动化交易"
msgstr "In the future, we will connect to brokers’ live trading interfaces via the QMT API to enable automated trading."

