msgid "![png](examples/img/trader_app_1.png)   ![png](examples/img/trader_app_2.png)   ![png](examples/img/trader_app_light_theme.png)"
msgstr "![png](examples/img/trader_app_1.png)   ![png](examples/img/trader_app_2.png)   ![png](examples/img/trader_app_light_theme.png)"

